    "Here we discuss the various types of data involved in student cognitive modeling.",
    "As shown in Fig. 2, the dataset includes the interactive records of students answering exercises, as well as the relationship information between the exercises and the KCs.",
    "Additionally, the features of students and exercises, as well as the relations among KCs, also contain rich information that can enhance the accuracy of modeling.",
    "Various models selectively utilize different features and data formats based on their requirements.• Student-side features typically include information about students' family background, school background, and other relevant factors.",
    "These pieces of information are valuable for modeling students' abilities as prior knowledge."
